

#intro_container

  .intro
    %h1 Rails Kitchen Sink
    %p.slogan 
      Everything you need, and nothing you don't.
    %p
      This demo is designed to provide a solid, generic 
      skeleton to base your next rails project on, and includes everything 
      you'll need to dive straight in and build your dream app.
    %p
      Built on HTML5 and Rails 3, 
      %em Rails Kitchen Sink
      is ready to rock.

#feature_container

  .feature#authentication
    %h2 Authentication
    %p 
      Includes registration, login, password-reset 
      and account-locking functionality thanks to&nbsp;
      %a{:href => 'http://github.com/plataformatec/devise'}> Devise
      \.

  .feature#user_management
    %h2 User Management
    %p 
      Admin users can use the built-in administration section to add,
      edit and delete users.
    
  .clear
    
  .feature#authorization
    %h2 Authorization
    %p 
      Simple authorization system based on&nbsp;
      %a{:href => 'http://github.com/ryanb/cancan'}> CanCan
      , which you can extend to meet your needs.
    
  .feature#future_proof
    %h2 Future Proof
    %p 
      We've done our best to use the current Rails 3 and HTML5 best practices.

.clear

